Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: New Hampshire, the political weathervane
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b043w1bs
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 24 Feb 1980
Why the weather is a factor in the New Hampshire primary 'beauty contest' stakes. The sound quality on this recording is variable/poor. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014. Show less